communications.subject: Kentucky Open Records Act Request: Untitled
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Kentucky Open Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Mileage, sign-out records, and maintenance logs for the following fleet vehicles:

Unit #	Year Model	Reg#	Color	VIN	Last 8
11-958	2011 Taurus	E6H240	Black	1FAHP2EW5BG148958	BG148958
13-286	2013 Taurus	E6H228	White	1FAHP2M88DG124286	DG124286
13-289	2013 Taurus	E6H232	White	1FAHP2M83DG124289	DG124289
13-756	2013 Explorer	H8P938	White	1FM5K8B85DGA46756	DGA46756
14-056	2014 Explorer	H8P935	Black	1FM5K8B87EGA92056	EGA92056
15-655	2015 Taurus	E6H229	Silver	1FAHP2MK1FG163655	FG163655
18-175	2018 Taurus	E6H231	White	1FAHP2MK9JG106175	JG106175
22-071	2022 Durango	E1C010	White	1C4RDJFGXNC137071	NC137071

Any records of approved or denied off-duty details,
any records of officers participating in approved off-duty details including which off-duty details each officer has participated in,
any records of compensation received by an officer by participating in off duty details,
any reported incidents concerning Audubon Park equipment or officers while being used in off-duty details
any policies, standards, request forms used by officers and administration to request, evaluate, approve, or deny off-duty details.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or to a USB flash drive if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

James Michael Hartman Jr
